trans-unit.source: A binding parameter that can be used with the HTTP Transport to specify the setting for HttpMessage support.
trans-unit.target: 可与 HTTP 传输协议一起使用的、用于指定 HttpMessage 支持的绑定参数。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpMessageSettings" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpMessageSettings" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: The object to compare with the current object.
trans-unit.target: 要与当前对象进行比较的对象。

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the specified Object is equal to the current Object.
trans-unit.target: 确定指定的对象是否等于当前对象。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the specified Object is equal to the current Object; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果指定的对象等于当前对象，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the HTTP transport should support <see cref="T:System.Net.Http.HttpRequestMessage" /> and <see cref="T:System.Net.Http.HttpResponseMessage" /> instances.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置指示 HTTP 传输是否应支持 <see cref="T:System.Net.Http.HttpRequestMessage" /> 和 <see cref="T:System.Net.Http.HttpResponseMessage" /> 实例的值。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the HTTP transport supports <see cref="T:System.Net.Http.HttpRequestMessage" /> and <see cref="T:System.Net.Http.HttpResponseMessage" /> instances; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 HTTP 传输支持 <see cref="T:System.Net.Http.HttpRequestMessage" /> 和 <see cref="T:System.Net.Http.HttpResponseMessage" /> 实例，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。
